                    "value": null,
                    "text": "L"
                },
                "text": "Explorer\u2019s clothing is sturdy enough that it can be reinforced to protect you, even though it isn\u2019t a suit of armor. It comes in many forms, though the most common sorts look like clerical vestments, monk\u2019s garments, or wizard\u2019s robes, as members of all three classes are likely to avoid wearing armor. For more information on explorer\u2019s clothing, see its entry in the armor category.",
